summary: Preset of Ororo Munroe (Storm) from the X-Men
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Georgia][color=#9fc5e8][size=5]
X-Men's Storm[/size][/color][/font][/center][font=Comic Sans MS]
[/font][center][font=Comic Sans MS]X-Men fan here, so I had to make a preset of my favorite wind rider and leader of the X-Men gold team.[/font][/center][font=Comic Sans MS][center]
Race:
[color=#ea9999]Nord[/color][/center]
My first preset either place in:
[color=#ea9999]Data/SKSE/CharGen/Presets
[/color]
or if using ModOrganizer Place in:
[color=#ea9999]Overwrite/SKSE/CharGen/Presets[/color]

Required files:
[list=1]
[*][color=#ea9999]SKSE[/color]
[*][color=#ea9999]Racemenu[/color]
[*][color=#ea9999]KS Hairdo - Renewal[/color]
[*][color=#ea9999]FSx - Sentiment Eyes[/color]
[*][color=#ea9999]SKY Female Textures[/color]

[/list][/font][font=Comic Sans MS]

[center]Special thanks to [b]al3xtaylor[/b] for providing the base to build this Preset. [/center][/font]
